12:00.754 --> 12:03.221
Oh... fuck.

12:04.725 --> 12:05.957
Fuck.

12:07.227 --> 12:08.293
Fuck!

12:12.165 --> 12:14.232
This is my friend... Philip.

12:14.234 --> 12:15.500
Yeah. Hi.

12:20.407 --> 12:22.073
I thought
you were bringing a girl.

12:24.044 --> 12:25.510
Not a fucking dude.

12:27.781 --> 12:31.883
Is this your uncle who got fired for being
a pediatrician that crossed the line?

12:31.885 --> 12:34.519
- Nope, that one just got out of jail.
- Okay.

12:34.521 --> 12:37.355
Well, is there any chance
we could stay with him?

12:39.259 --> 12:41.159
I'm guessing that's a no.

12:43.130 --> 12:44.529
- Okay.
- Well.

12:45.465 --> 12:47.632
Oh. Porno. Great.

12:51.705 --> 12:54.038
He used to have
the dopest place in the city,

12:54.040 --> 12:57.208
but I guess catching your wife bang your
best friend can really screw a guy up.

12:57.210 --> 12:59.110
Eesh. Someone married that guy?

12:59.112 --> 13:00.745
Yeah. There's hope for you yet.

13:00.747 --> 13:02.380
Yeah, I don't need hope.

13:02.382 --> 13:03.681
Do you two know what you want?

13:04.217 --> 13:06.251
Uh, are you on the menu?

13:06.253 --> 13:08.219
Ha. Not too good with
the ladies, are you?

13:08.221 --> 13:11.189
- Figure out what you want.
- My shift ends in five minutes.

13:12.225 --> 13:13.558
That's not an invitation.

13:13.560 --> 13:16.694
Uh, I think it was.

13:18.064 --> 13:20.565
What do you think she meant when she
said I wasn't good with the ladies?

13:20.567 --> 13:22.400
That meant that she was
obviously flirting with me.

13:22.402 --> 13:25.303
Great, now you can finally
forget about Allison.

13:42.956 --> 13:44.255
Holy shit!

13:44.257 --> 13:45.924
Well, this is awkward.

13:45.926 --> 13:47.492
That's my dad.

13:47.494 --> 13:49.994
Hawaiian shirt,
headed straight for us!

13:51.431 --> 13:53.191
How did he find us?
You said he was in Japan.

13:53.366 --> 13:55.033
