13:55.702 --> 13:56.702
Come on.

13:59.439 --> 14:00.572
Your jacket.

14:02.876 --> 14:04.309
Okay, here's your salad.

14:04.311 --> 14:05.877
Can I get you
anything else with that?

14:05.879 --> 14:07.946
- Excuse me.
- Oh, my gosh!

14:07.948 --> 14:09.447
Are you okay? Oh, my God.

14:09.449 --> 14:11.249
I'm sorry,
did that spill on you?

14:33.874 --> 14:35.773
Do you think he saw us?

14:39.312 --> 14:41.246
I don't think it's you
he's looking for.

14:46.887 --> 14:48.353
We... We have to follow them.

14:48.355 --> 14:50.255
- Come on!
- What? No, we don't!

14:52.058 --> 14:53.391
Don't get too close.

14:56.830 --> 15:01.532
You know, they say men your father's age
cheat to make themselves feel younger.

15:01.534 --> 15:04.669
She's our age!
How young is he trying to feel?

15:04.671 --> 15:05.437
I don't know.

15:05.449 --> 15:07.005
Yeah, yeah, hold it.
Pull over right here.

15:07.007 --> 15:08.367
- Here?
- Yeah, yeah, stop.

15:11.177 --> 15:12.410
Turn off the car.

15:16.883 --> 15:20.518
There could be a hundred reasons
why an older man would spend time

15:20.520 --> 15:21.819
with an attractive young girl.

15:22.956 --> 15:24.055
Like?

15:24.057 --> 15:25.256
Like...

15:26.026 --> 15:29.427
wild, crazy, horrifying sex.

15:30.030 --> 15:31.195
I was joking.

15:31.197 --> 15:33.264
Oh, no, Philip!
No, no, bad, bad...

15:33.867 --> 15:35.033
Dude! Dude!

15:35.035 --> 15:39.103
Dude, we need to get out of here.
Seriously, do you want to get caught!

15:43.376 --> 15:45.843
What kind of sick shit's
going on in here?

15:50.116 --> 15:51.282
Come on.

15:52.719 --> 15:53.719
Come on!

16:03.663 --> 16:04.963
What are you doing?

16:04.965 --> 16:06.831
I got to find out somehow.

16:06.833 --> 16:10.368
Dude, dude, I saw my parents having
sex once, and it ruined me for life.

16:22.082 --> 16:23.748
- Hey, honey.
- Hey, Mom.

16:25.118 --> 16:27.218
- How was work?
- It was okay.

16:30.256 --> 16:33.257
Where is she? There's my woman.

16:33.259 --> 16:35.760
My woman, my woman, my...

16:35.762 --> 16:38.196
Hello, my man.
I'm so happy you're home.

16:38.198 --> 16:39.530
I missed...

16:39.532 --> 16:41.766
- Are you more beautiful?
- Hey, Dad!

16:41.768 --> 16:43.267
- What the hell?
- Uh-oh.

16:43.269 --> 16:46.437
Here you go, here you go.

16:46.439 --> 16:48.673
Is this my son or my son?

16:52.679 --> 16:56.814
Oh! It is...
It's so good to be home.

16:56.816 --> 16:58.983
- It's good to have you home.
- Right?

16:58.985 --> 16:59.653
Yeah.

16:59.665 --> 17:01.705
I mean, I love
Japan, but it's just like...

17:04.290 --> 17:06.357
Are you okay?

17:09.996 --> 17:13.765
Philip! Philip, what's going on?

17:14.800 --> 17:17.402
Philip, stop. Stop!
I can't bail you out of jail!

17:18.171 --> 17:20.038
Philip! Stop, stop!

17:20.040 --> 17:21.906
Lewis, he's not just cheating!

17:25.011 --> 17:26.411
He has a second family.

17:26.713 --> 17:28.246
Oh...

17:30.316 --> 17:32.884
Well, if at first
you don't succeed?

17:47.333 --> 17:49.233
Mom, does this red look
bloody to you?

17:49.235 --> 17:50.401
Mm-hmm.

17:51.204 --> 17:52.937
Mom! A little help here.

17:52.939 --> 17:54.705
Oh, sorry. Uh...

17:54.707 --> 17:59.277
Uh, bloody? Yes, it is very bloody.
It's like a crime scene.

18:18.031 --> 18:19.964
You know, this is nice.

18:19.966 --> 18:21.432
