- This.

18:22.268 --> 18:25.837
Just you and me. It's quiet.

18:26.272 --> 18:27.705
Eerily so.

18:27.707 --> 18:30.608
You know, you are gonna
have to get used to this.

18:30.610 --> 18:34.011
When your brother goes away to
college, it's just gonna be you and me.

18:35.482 --> 18:38.950
