19:35.341 --> 19:36.674
Oh, fuck.

19:38.144 --> 19:39.377
Fuck.

19:40.446 --> 19:42.413
Morning.

19:45.285 --> 19:47.051
Yeah, I'm not hungry.

19:47.053 --> 19:48.352
Me neither.

20:01.534 --> 20:03.534
All right, you know what, Phil?
I've been thinking.

20:05.038 --> 20:09.373
Maybe this shit with your dad is the best
thing that could've ever happened to you.

20:09.375 --> 20:11.742
- How's that?
- You finally found your dad's Kryptonite!

20:11.744 --> 20:13.644
No more curfews,
no more groundings,

20:13.646 --> 20:15.646
you can get anything
you want from him.

20:15.648 --> 20:17.315
You should ask for a car!

20:17.317 --> 20:19.550
